{"article_id":"ULmVy4YVUU8ypWx4","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Hagel ' s nomination now proceeds to the Senate floor .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"|","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"John Shinkle/","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Hagel nomination clears Senate committee","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Splitting along party lines ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"the Senate Armed Services Committee voted 14-11 on Tuesday to advance Chuck Hagel ' s nomination after a tense two-hour meeting","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"that closed the latest chapter in a weeks-long political saga .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"The nomination heads to the full Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"where Republicans may demand a 60-vote threshold in a vote","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"expected later this week .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Democrats and Republicans broke sharply over whether the former Republican senator from Nebraska is the right man","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"to run the Pentagon .","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"Supporters cited Hagel ' s experience as an enlisted soldier in Vietnam and his service in the Senate and elsewhere as reasons","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"he should succeed Defense Secretary Leon Panetta","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"while opponents stuck with their criticisms about Hagel ' s past positions on Iran , Israel and the defense budget .","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"A few Republicans kept up their bid","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"to stop Hagel ' s nomination from moving ahead ,","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"arguing","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"he has kept some information from the committee ,","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"but Democrats insisted","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"that he has satisfied its disclosure requirements","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"and accused Republicans of tarring Hagel unfairly .","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"Sen. Bill Nelson","depth":15},{"id":23,"text":"( D-Fla. )","depth":15},{"id":24,"text":"said","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"Sen. Ted Cruz","depth":16},{"id":26,"text":"( R-Texas )","depth":16},{"id":27,"text":"had `` gone over the line ''","depth":15},{"id":28,"text":"and `` basically ... impugned the patriotism of the nominee \"","depth":15},{"id":29,"text":"by pointing out","depth":16},{"id":30,"text":"that the Iranian Foreign Ministry had praised Hagel .","depth":16},{"id":31,"text":"The top Republican on the committee , Sen. Jim Inhofe","depth":15},{"id":32,"text":"( R-Okla. ) ,","depth":15},{"id":33,"text":"shot back later in defense of Cruz ,","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"`` You do n't get any cozier than that . ''","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"Former ranking member Sen. John McCain","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"( R-Ariz. )","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"interjected soon thereafter with a message for his colleagues :","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"`` Sen. Hagel is an honorable man","depth":15},{"id":39,"text":"who has served his country ,","depth":15},{"id":40,"text":"and no one on this committee at any time should impugn his character , ''","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"McCain said .","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"But for most of the meeting , senators referred to Hagel ' s late January confirmation hearing .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"McCain slammed Hagel ' s performance as \" the worst","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"I have seen of any nomination for office \"","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"and said","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"it was \" disturbing \" that Hagel would not directly respond to his question","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"about whether the Iraq surge was a success .","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"Democrats said","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"the criticism of Hagel ' s day in the spotlight was unfair ,","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"and they defended his description of a policy of \" containment \" for a nuclear Iran","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"- which the White House does not support -","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"as a simple slip of the tongue .","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"Apart from the politics","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"involved with Hagel himself ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Senate Armed Services Committee Chairman Carl Levin","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"( D-Mich. )","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"had warned senators","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"that rejecting him would endanger the Pentagon at a time","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"it could ill afford another complication .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"\" If there ' s a risk here ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"it is that the defeat of this nomination would leave the Department of Defense leaderless at a time","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"when we face immense budgetary challenges","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"and our military is engaged in combat operations overseas , ''","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"Levin said .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"While he acknowledged","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"that many senators oppose President Barack Obama 's foreign policy ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"`` our vote on Sen. Hagel 's nomination will not change those policies . ''","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"The meeting ultimately proved civil","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"compared with what might have been","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"-","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Republican aides had suggested earlier","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"that some GOP senators were considering walking out","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"to protest what they called Hagel ' s insufficient financial disclosures .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Inhofe and Cruz later ruled that out .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"anything is gained by theatrics , \"","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Cruz told .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Just the same , Republicans continued to try to put on the brakes .","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"Louisiana Sen. David Vitter quarreled with Levin over what Vitter said","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"was an incomplete disclosure from Hagel of past speeches ,","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"and Cruz renewed the GOP line","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"of questioning","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"about whether Hagel had taken payments from \" foreign sources . \"","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Hagel ' s nomination now proceeds to the Senate floor ,","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"where Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"( D-Nev. )","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"has said","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"he hopes","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"the chamber could vote on it Wednesday or Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"Some Republicans said","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"they might continue to oppose Hagel before the full Senate ,","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"but Reid responded with a single word on Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"when asked","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"whether he ' d honor an attempt at a hold :","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"\" No . \"","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"With 55 Democrats","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"controlling the Senate","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"and two Republicans","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"- Mike Johanns of Nebraska and Thad Cochran of Mississippi -","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"already publicly supporting Hagel ,","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"only three more Republicans would need to support him for confirmation under a request from Republicans for a 60-vote threshold .","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"Inhofe said Monday night","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"that he would not use his privilege","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"to delay Hagel ' s confirmation into the weekend or early next week ,","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"so long as Democrats produced 60 votes upfront","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"to support Hagel .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"This article first appeared on Pro at 5:05 p.m. on February 12 , 2013 .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":215,"left":214,"right":107,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":191,"right":213,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},